event.title: After Work
event.description:
Unwind and Connect at After Work
Step out of the office and into a relaxing evening of good vibes, music, and great company. After Work is your midweek escape — a casual yet vibrant gathering where professionals and creatives come together to network, recharge, and celebrate the day’s wins. Whether you're here for the drinks, the conversations, or the music, this is your space to unwind, meet new people, and enjoy the evening — no suits required.
